Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here's my new weapon, Kuwagata!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you all set, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, but I only made this to look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea how it will actually work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Aim for the \Ncenter of that lug's gut!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Special Attack! Iron Man Comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this, Moria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not done yet, Oars.\NHe's still hanging on by a thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That cloud...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did they do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Quit yelling my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.12,0:04:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if he notices me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? What? What?! Can he stretch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-His arm extended?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stretched. That feels \Nmore like how it should.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Straw Hat Crew Gets Wiped Out!\NThe Shadow-Shadow's Powers in Full Swing!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.67,0:05:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the groove now that my body stretches.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes another attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His attack power has skyrocketed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come Oars can stretch\Nwhen he isn't a power holder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Moria do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good guess! I'm making you live this\Nnightmare with my Shadow-Shadow power...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Shadow Revolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Revolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:07:00.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadows copy whatever your body does.\NThat's common knowledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your body and shadow are always\Nmirror images of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a hard-and-fast rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars' shadow is supposed to obey him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I usurped control by\Nslipping my shadow inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that means?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can freely alter the shape of Oars' shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But his shadow and body\Nmust take the same form.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the shadow stops\Nmatching the shape of his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his body transforms to match his shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how Shadow Revolution works!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's the\Nopposite of common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria made the arms and legs\Nin Oars' shadow extend,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so his body stretched to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So instead of becoming a rubber man,\NOars' body can transform into anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break. He's too big for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I can't get near him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is far worse than rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make his shadow round...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars will turn into a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! Just a sec, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.18,0:08:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep out of my fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bad! I didn't mean to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just here to offer assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Oars! Crush each\Nand every one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where is Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria must have tricked him\Ninto going somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way he got his butt kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? I swear, he is such an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? Should I tell everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already in a tight spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they need to know
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there is another Warlord \Non this island right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So does this mean everyone\Nwon't get their shadows back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless we defeat both Zombie Luffy and Moria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! It's almost dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of the enemy's plan!\NWe just have to thwart it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Excuse me!\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton, you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please grant me this one request!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.50,0:10:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get near him, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you see what happened to Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me for what happens!\NThis packs a wallop, so get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Cloud Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead! Please do your thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd use Kuwagata again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no greater pain than\Nbeing unable to repay a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.42,0:10:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall put in backbreaking effort!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then off you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slalom Vine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The electricity is so strong\Nyou can see my bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was nothing but bones to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's show time! I'm like a lightning arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning Bone Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gavotte Bond en Avant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! He drilled through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went through my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made an opening! Keep the attacks going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission: Complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style... Nigiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Tower Climb!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you--no, first I'm going\Nto finish off that skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He wouldn't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:12:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack! Atlas Comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Crap!\N--Usopp, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fight"? Eh? Hey! Whoa, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're up next, Long Nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My arm isn't stretching! Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochenta Fleurs Cuatro Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did these arms come from?!\NThey're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.32,0:13:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop manipulating\Nhis shadow for the time being?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gak! C-Can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this will \Nkeep me out of the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your plan doesn't amuse me in the least!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brick Bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Veinte Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calendula!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:14:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.04,0:14:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're \Ndoing to Robin-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.11,0:14:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria's shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see who is the more powerful\Nlong-distance power holder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hold hurts pretty darn bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get distracted by his shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we take out his body,\Nthe shadow will disappear as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuatro Mano!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sweet!\N--You're amazing, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Robin! Watch out\Nfor the shadow behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is Moria doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were close! It's such a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doppelman and I can switch\Nplaces at any given minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They switched places?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then the one inside Oars is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Shadow Substitute that\Nhas no joints to dislocate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.26,0:16:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! It's the shadow that\Nwas here until just a second ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's three down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.65,0:17:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's got Robin's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.20,0:17:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything to put it in,\Nbut I might as well take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.42,0:17:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give Robin-chan's shadow back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra Haché!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brick Bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He switched places with his shadow again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he switched with his shadow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moria is back inside Oars' stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everything has returned to how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh darn it, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is supposed to be my fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Oars. I had a bit\Ntoo much fun with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish off that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His arms can stretch out again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! He's going to attack\NRobin when she's out cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Robin! Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frit Assorti!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.18,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You repelled him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance!\NGet Robin-chan away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sanji! Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, what are you doing up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been searching for what\Ncaused Oars to die 500 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His cause of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after his right arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't his real arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hogback reconstructed it, but there are signs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nof horrible frostbite around the stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say for certain, but I suspect\Nhe froze to death 500 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a monster like this is\Nno match for the elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:20:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He died while wandering the Land of Ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.44,0:20:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even 500 years ago,\NI'd wager Oars went around...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...mostly naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.11,0:20:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna lose to someone that stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies may not feel pain,\Nbut they still take damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.20,0:20:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the attacks we've\Nlanded are accumulating!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can render this arm nonfunctional,\Nit will halve his offensive power!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, focus on this one arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you talking up a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.01,0:20:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while standing on my shoulder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a zombie,\Nyou have no idea how badly
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.65,0:20:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you just hurt your own body\Nwith that punch, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.91,0:20:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, you went inside my fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:21:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh! I'm tiny, so the crevices\Nin your fist are like caves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.13,0:21:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arm Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you dodged that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lend you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armée de l'Air...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cloven...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.97,0:21:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roseo Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop hitting me in the same spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those attacks aren't going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll work! Pain is a signal\Nmeant to protect the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lacking pain doesn't make you strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.14,0:21:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save your fuzzy logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.31,0:22:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That looks bad, guys!\NGet away from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.02,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're in for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.90,0:22:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.23,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There go another two...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's taking everyone out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:23:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four down! Five down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.30,0:23:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea who you are,\Nbut thanks for rescuing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.80,0:23:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're stinking strong now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.02,0:23:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Incredible Battle \NStarts! Luffy vs. Luffy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
